name: Ankita Classic Warkhand Road

reviews.review_text: The prawns in the starters were enjoyable, but unfortunately, the mix fried rice contained artificial prawns instead of real ones, which was disappointing. The overall experience was below average as the hospitality was not up to the mark. While some dishes were decent, the food quality overall left room for improvement.

A Must-Visit Gem on Warkhand Road – Ankita Classic!

While traveling from Goa towards Maharashtra, we stumbled upon Ankita Classic on Warkhand Road, and it turned out to be the highlight of our journey! From the moment we stepped in, it was a delightful experience, thanks to the warm hospitality of Host Rahul Dalvi, who made us feel right at home.

The seafood is nothing short of awesome – fresh, flavorful, and perfectly cooked! The portions were generous, and the pricing was unbelievably reasonable for the quality and quantity we received.

The interiors are simply outstanding – a visual treat! It’s rare to find such a beautifully designed space along the highway. With a seating capacity of over 350 people, it’s perfect for large gatherings, yet cozy enough for a family meal.

Parking is often a challenge on long road trips, but not here – there’s ample parking space to accommodate vehicles of all sizes.

If you’re a seafood lover and appreciate great ambiance, Ankita Classic is a must-visit. It’s more than just a restaurant; it’s an experience you’ll cherish! Don’t miss this gem if you’re traveling in the area.

I visited this place twice and it was fantastic. Large parking space, good ambience, staffs behaviour was good all are cooperative. I tasted 10 different types of fishes here and all were good in taste. Actually I ordered starters those were good in taste and later ordered thali. Thali was good but not able to finish full thali because it was too big. So I would suggest if you order starters then surely go for small thali and share big thali because lots of food will waste later. So, I would suggest you should visit this place once if you are seafood lover and it is affordable not too costly.

description:
### Discovering Coastal Flavors at Ankita Classic on Warkhand Road

Nestled within the bustling Corlim Industrial Estate, **Ankita Classic** stands out as a culinary gem, boasting an impressive **rating of 4.5** from **3,650 enthusiastic reviews**. This beloved eatery has captured the hearts of diners with its **seafood specialties**, notably the much-celebrated **fish thali**, along with delicious offerings of **kingfish** and **squid** dishes. The abundance of feedback underlines its status as a top-notch seafood destination, clearly mirrored in the frequency of tags: **seafood (300)**, **fish thali (50)**, **kingfish (26)**, and **squids (22)**.

### Ambiance & Design

Stepping into Ankita Classic is akin to entering a warm and inviting sanctuary. The restaurant boasts an aesthetically pleasing decor that merges modern design with coastal vibes. **Vibrant colors and elegant furnishings** create a welcoming atmosphere, perfect for both intimate dinners and larger gatherings. The spacious layout accommodates up to **350 diners**, ensuring that both families and groups can enjoy their meal without feeling cramped. **Natural lighting** bathes the space during the day, while soft, ambient music enhances the overall dining experience, as noted by patrons in their reviews. Images capturing this inviting ambiance reveal stylish furnishings and a carefully curated interior that contribute to its charm, inviting guests to linger.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Ankita Classic's menu is a treasure trove for seafood enthusiasts. Reviewers rave about the **freshness and flavor** of the dishes, particularly highlighting the tender **prawns** that grace the starters. The **fish thali** is a standout for its generous portions; a bountiful assortment of seafood served beautifully on a platter ensures that each diner can savor a range of delightful flavors. For those unsure of their capacity, one patron astutely recommends opting for a smaller thali when indulging in multiple starters, echoing the sentiments of a thoughtful dining experience to prevent food wastage. Today’s seafood fare also extends to **squid** and several types of **fish**, ensuring variety to please even the most discerning palates. 

### Customer Experience & Service

Customer service at Ankita Classic enjoys its fair share of commendation, with many reviewers emphasizing the **attentiveness** and **friendliness** of the staff. Host **Rahul Dalvi** received notable mention for his hospitality, making guests feel at home from the moment they arrive. While some reviews noted isolated instances of inconsistent food quality, the overall sentiment leans positively towards service efficiency and attentiveness. Reviewers appreciate the **ample parking** available for visitors, an often overlooked but essential detail for travelers stopping amidst a long journey.

### Popularity & Reviews

Ankita Classic has not only captured the attention of local diners but has also garnered a reputation beyond the locale as a **must-visit venue** for those traveling along the route. The blend of **affordable pricing** and high-quality offerings resonates well, creating a buzz on social media and dining platforms alike. Comparative analysis of customer reviews reflects a diverse range of experiences, with recommendations highlighting this restaurant as an invaluable stop for those who appreciate seafood in a beautiful setting.

### Utilizing Visual Content

The visual narrative provided through various **customer photographs** further solidifies Ankita Classic’s appeal. From snapshots of lavish seafood platters showcasing the wonderfully presented dishes to images of the inviting decor, it is evident that this establishment strikes that perfect balance between flavor and aesthetics. The warm and vibrant tones of the interior, intertwined with the enticing visuals of succulent seafood, create a testament to the dining experience that awaits future visitors.

In conclusion, Ankita Classic is not just a restaurant; it represents a delightful voyage for the senses—perfectly seasoned seafood, a breathtaking ambiance, and a welcoming staff harmonize. Whether you are a local or a traveler on a journey, this spot promises an experience you won't easily forget. Don’t skip the opportunity to indulge in one of the finest seafood offerings in the region.
